<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[الشين والذال]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">رَجُلٌ شِنْذَارَةٌ:</span> للفاحِشِ،<span class="c5"> وشِنْذِيْرَةٌ:</span> مِثْلُه.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الشَّبَرْذَاةُ:</span> النّاقَةُ السَّرِيْعَةُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">ورَجُلٌ شَبَرْذَى:</span> وهو السَّرِيْعُ في أُمُوْرِه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">عليه شِرْذِبَةٌ من مالٍ وشِرْذِمَةٌ:</span> أي قَلِيلٌ منه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">والشِّرْذِمَةُ:</span> القِطْعَةُ من الشَّيْءِ حَتّى النّاس.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">والشَّمَيْذَرُ:</span> السَّرِيْعُ من الإِبل، والأُنْثى شَمَيْذَرَةٌ، وكذلك الشَّمْذَرُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وسَيْرٌ شَمَيْذَرٌ:</span> سَرِيْعٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">ونَاقَةٌ شَمَرْذَاةٌ:</span> للسَّرِيْعَةِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>